Respected enthusiasts of home brewing and beer aficionados, get ready because SMASH 2024 homebrew competition for home brewers is coming to Split on May 4th! This year's, fourth in a row, competition brings several novelties. Registration for the competition opens on February 15, 2024, and we bring you all you need to know about the competition, how to sign up as a participant, and win rich prizes.
