&nbsp;  
# How to Register for the SMASH Homebrew Competition?
At the SMASH homebrew competition, each registered participant needs to brew beer with one type of malt and one type of hops (single malt & single hop), chosen exclusively at home. This year, participants can sign up for TWO beer styles: 3A Czech Pale Lager and 18B American Pale Ale! In previous years, there was only one style, but this year we're taking it a step further. – says the SMASH team.
&nbsp;  
## 3A Czech Pale Lager:
Pilsner malt
Saaz hops
Yeast of choice
&nbsp;  
## 18B American Pale Ale:
Pale Ale malt
Amarillo hops
Yeast of choice
&nbsp;  
![smash-4.webp](https://udruzenje-kucnih-pivara-srbije.s3.eu-central-1.amazonaws.com/smash_4_2b735209df.webp)
&nbsp;  
Organizers Ivana, Diano, Pave, and Riža, after last year's record-breaking 60 international applications received in one day, again expect all applications to be received on the same day. This year, they have a new online registration system, so they hope the website won't crash. A novelty is that this year judges and assistants can also register online. All information about the competition rules, guidelines, and registration procedures can be found on their website: [SMASH registration](https://smash-homebrew.com.hr/Registration/)
&nbsp;  
# Styles and Prizes for this Year's SMASH Competition
In addition to styles, they've also increased the prizes. The best beers at the competition, Best of Show (BOS), will be awarded with a BrewTaurus FlexiTaurus PF30L fermenter worth 700 euros. Participants will have the opportunity to win fantastic prizes, including Brodić-promet medals for the top three places.
&nbsp;  
## 3A Czech Pale Lager prizes:
First place wins a Duofiller can filler, a Yakima Chief Hops gift package, a Lallemand Brewing gift package, a BarthHaas X gift package, an All for Beer gift card worth €80, 25kg of Pilsner malt, a Badass Barley Malt T-shirt, five T-shirts with custom designs from Lumer Shop, a CroCraft beer package, a Juta Spiza gift package, and personalized beer coasters from Sticker Mule.
&nbsp;  
The second prize will take home a Yakima Chief Hops gift package, a Lallemand Brewing gift package, a BarthHaas X gift package, an All for Beer gift card worth €50, a €50 gift card and a glass package from NIRS, 25kg of Pilsner malt, a Badass Barley Malt T-shirt, five T-shirts with custom designs from Lumer Shop, 10 beers from CroCraft, and a Juta Spiza gift package.
&nbsp;  
The third prize wins a Yakima Chief Hops gift package, a Lallemand Brewing gift package, a BarthHaas X gift package, an All for Beer gift card worth €20, 25kg of Pilsner malt, a hoodie with Badass Barley Malt along with the hoodie, five T-shirts with custom designs from Lumer Shop, 10 beers from CroCraft, and a Juta Spiza gift package.
&nbsp;  
## 18B American Pale Ale prizes:
First place wins a Tilt hydrometer wireless device for measuring beer density and temperature, a Yakima Chief Hops gift package, a Lallemand Brewing gift package, a BarthHaas X gift package, an All for Beer gift card worth €80, 25kg of Pilsner malt, a Badass Barley Malt T-shirt, five T-shirts with custom designs from Lumer Shop, a CroCraft beer package, a Juta Spiza gift package, and personalized beer coasters from Sticker Mule.
&nbsp;  
The second prize will take home a Yakima Chief Hops gift package, a Lallemand Brewing gift package, a BarthHaas X gift package, an All for Beer gift card worth €50, a €50 gift card and a glass package from NIRS, 25kg of Pilsner malt, a Badass Barley Malt T-shirt, five T-shirts with custom designs from Lumer Shop, 10 beers from CroCraft, and a Juta Spiza gift package.
&nbsp;  
The third prize wins a Yakima Chief Hops gift package, a Lallemand Brewing gift package, a BarthHaas X gift package, an All for Beer gift card worth €20, 25kg of Pilsner malt, a hoodie with Badass Barley Malt along with the hoodie, five T-shirts with custom designs from Lumer Shop, 10 beers from CroCraft, and a Juta Spiza gift package.
&nbsp;  
Don't miss the opportunity to showcase your skills and win great prizes.
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
# What Will the Main SMASH Event on May 4th Look Like?
This year, the entire event will take place in just one day, on May 4th. In the morning, from early morning hours, the judging of registered beers will take place. It is possible that some of the participants of the Course for Training Beer Judges will judge at SMASH for the first time.
&nbsp;  
The grand announcement of the SMASH homebrew 2023 winners and award ceremony will be held in the evening at BackPLAN B Pub in Split.
&nbsp;  
– We had the impression that last year, when we organized SMASH for two consecutive days, some teams missed each other. Our goal is to have all brewers together and exchange experiences at all levels. – says Diano.
&nbsp;  
This event promises an unforgettable day filled with beer tasting, great music, and endless fun! Will you sign up? Rich prizes await you.
